				<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8fc0fd4d51a6c89040faa00c37c2b655?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8fc0fd4d51a6c89040faa00c37c2b655?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn">Sarah</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
