				<div class="comment-body"><p>Norm:</p>
<p>The works are defined by word length in the <a href="http://www.wsfs.org/bm/const-2006.html#hugo" rel="nofollow">WSFS Constitution</a>:</p>
<p>Novel: 40,000 words or longer<br />
Novella: 15,000 &#8211; 40,000 words<br />
Novelette: 7,500 &#8211; 15,000 words<br />
Short Story: Under 7,500 words</p>
<p>&#8211; Kevin Standlee</p>
</div>

