<p>See our <a href="../../index.html?page_id=5" rel="nofollow">Frequently Asked Questions</a> page under the heading &#8220;Why are they called Hugos?&#8221;</p>
<p>The awards are named for Hugo Gernsback, an important figure in the early days of modern science fiction.</p>
<p>&#8212; Kevin Standlee</p>
