				<div class="comment-body"><p>When does the short list come out for the best novel?</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=231#respond' data-commentid="231" data-postid="11" data-belowelement="comment-231" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to Kevin Q.'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
