				<div class="comment-body"><p>I&#8217;m trying to persuade a fanfic site that it would be a good idea to have a &#8220;no award&#8221; choice on their annual awards poll. This seems to work well for the Hugos, and I think it would improve the overall quality of the winners on the fanfic site.</p>
<p>When was it first added as an option on the Hugo ballots?</p>
