				<div class="comment-body"><p>Charron,</p>
<p>We can&#8217;t find any NAACP award by that name but the NAACP does award the Spingarn Medal annually for outstanding achievement by a African American.<br />
See <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spingarn_Medal" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spingarn_Medal</a></p>
<p>The NAACP also runs the Image Awards for dramatic works: <a href="http://www.naacpimageawards.net/40/index.php" rel="nofollow">http://www.naacpimageawards.net/40/index.php</a></p>
<p>&#8211; Vincent Docherty</p>
</div>

